## ğŸ§© **What is a Pushdown Automaton (PDA)?**

A **Pushdown Automaton (PDA)** is like a **Finite Automaton (FA)** but with an extra memory structure â€” a **stack**.

ğŸ‘‰ This makes PDA more powerful than FA and allows it to recognize **Context-Free Languages (CFLs)**.

