Where:

| Symbol | Meaning                                            |
| ------ | -------------------------------------------------- |
| **Q**  | Set of finite states                               |
| **Î£**  | Input alphabet                                     |
| **Î“**  | Stack alphabet (symbols that can be pushed/popped) |
| **Î´**  | Transition function                                |
| **qâ‚€** | Start state                                        |
| **Zâ‚€** | Initial symbol on stack (bottom marker)            |
